submitPaymentRequests.t.sol
├─ given the contract is paused
│  └─ it should revert
└─ given the contract is not paused
   ├─ when the payment request list is empty
   │  └─ it should revert
   └─ when the payment request list is not empty
      ├─ when the funding address is the zero address
      │  └─ it should revert
      └─ when the funding address is not the zero address
         ├─ when the payment request is expired
         │  └─ it should revert
         └─ when the payment request is not expired
            ├─ when the token amounts list is empty
            │  └─ it should revert
            └─ when the token amounts list is not empty
               ├─ when the payment request signature is not valid
               │  └─ it should revert
               └─ when the payment request signature is valid
                  ├─ when the amount of tokens to transfer is zero
                  │  └─ it should revert
                  └─ when the amount of tokens to transfer is greater than zero
                     ├─ it should set add the payment request ID to the list of submitted payment requests
                     └─ it should emit a PaymentRequestSubmitted event
